/*--------------------------------*- Choupo -*-----------------------*\
  propertyPackage (INLINE) -- COSMO-SAC 2002 activity model over five common
  compounds whose sigma profiles live in their data/standards component files
  (cosmo{} block, VT-2005 / NIST benchmark).  No pair parameters: the mixture
  non-ideality comes entirely from the sigma profiles.
\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
components       ( water ethanol acetone nHexane toluene );
activityModel    { model cosmoSAC; }
equationOfState  { model idealGas; }
